can easily apply filters to search through all of your documents by keywords or creation dates. Ulysses is a great program for Type-A writers or those who are always on the go.","The creative writing program goes above and beyond to create a clean, distraction-free interface for its users. You can opt for a split-screen view, wherein you can see your text, notes and folders in one view, or just your text. It even offers a typewriter mode so that whatever you’re currently typing is vertically fixed to the top, center or bottom, depending on your preferences. Beyond that, Ulysses also lets you customize the theme, and you can navigate it using only keyboard shortcuts.","Before you finalize and send off your story, Ulysses can help you edit your document’s grammar and appearance. You can customize the font type, size, emphasis and spacing. Headers, footers, page numbers and other attributes are also easy to insert and customize.","Ulysses is only available for Mac OS X 10.6.6+ users or those with iOS devices. You can contact the company’s support team via email, or peruse the knowledgebase and tutorials if you want to troubleshoot something on your own."]},"id":"8eebc656-b605-42d0-845f-27fa74d6b19f","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"305e580a-65e8-4423-983e-1934c0e2dc23","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Although Ulysses is a sleek, easy-to-navigate program, and has extensive options for synchronization, document management, productivity, and even importing and exporting, it falls incredibly short in terms of its story outline and development tools."]},"id":"43051c4c-3ab7-4a7d-bdbd-0717ccb1dd42","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_69594","url":"/ulysses-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"suzanne-humphries","url":"/author/suzanne-humphries","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Suzanne Humphries","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"5Cbzn8X4VHCDchbqEBVidP","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"terri